thread.title: Swift CEO: Cyber security a bigger challenge than fintech
thread.title_full: Swift CEO: Cyber security a bigger challenge than fintech

author: Financial News
title: Swift CEO: Cyber security a bigger challenge than fintech
text:
Special Report: FN at Sibos 2015 Cyber security is a “major issue” and should be viewed as more of a pressing challenge for banks than disruption from fintech even though some new technologies such as blockchain are here to stay, according to Gottfried Leibbrandt, the chief executive of payments network Swift.
